Builds:
- node app.js dev
    - Listens to port 8083 in DEV environment
- npm run-script build && node app.js prod
    - Listens to port 8082 in PROD environment
- npm run-script build && node app.js all
    - Listens to both 8083 in DEV and 8082 in PROD

Firewall commands:
- firewall-cmd --permanent --add-port=xxxx/tcp
- firewall-cmd --reload
- firewall-cmd --list-ports

